<br>
It is only the choice of those placing the labels to do so.<br>
<br>
I am a person of principle.  Remember, we are all people behind this keyboard.  I chose to live my live the way I do.  Racism and bigotry are not a part of my life, and it sickens me to see people label others with such hatred.  Everquest alows people to escape that form of bigotry and hatred, by allowing people to play a game in virtual anonimity.<br>
<br>
I don't expect people to be easily forgiving about the Sleeper being Awakened.<br>
<br>
But the victims of racism and bigotry can not be blamed for the cruel actions of the racist.  It is by your choice that you hate us.  You can chose to not hate us as well.  Which choice is the one of principle? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=usildordhujata>Usildor Dhujata</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 138<br> <font color=#330000>(6/23/03 11:55 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/poeticsarcasm/images/marblemn.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Please</span><hr size=1> Racism and bigotry?  YOu absolutely disgust me by attemping to align your issue with those.  The victims of racism are the victims of hatred by no action of their own, by no fault of their own.  YOur guild did something that negatively affected the server and you support them.  You should be absolutely ashamed to try to pitch that argument.  Give me a fucking break. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.aol.com/poeticsarcasm/images/eodsig.jpg" style="border:0;height:200;width:500;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
