<br>
I'm sorry, but to compare the likes of THIS to racism and bigotry is not only flawed but also offensive.<br>
<br>
As much as I can't stand racist people, there are a lot of factors to their views such as sheer ignorance and family upbringing and education.  They're prevelent in today's society and even though we've come a long way, it still exist.  People are still racist because of different hues or accents.<br>
<br>
I've dealt with this first hand when I had to leave a girl that didn't want to let her parents know about our relationship because she's white and I'm black and her father just happened to be one of the members of the House of Respresentatives in my state.  To quote her, &quot;It wouldn't look good for him.&quot;  Yeah it sucked.  But oh well, c'est la vie.<br>
<br>
But what Hawkestone did was not out of ignorance or mis-education or even out of sheer stupidity.  It was deliberate.  Granted, I can't place the label on every single person in that guild because I don't care that much to place everyone in that guild on ignore.  On that same coin, I just won't speak to someone from the guild unless I've known them from way back (and even then I'd probably question their outlook on the whole ordeal). If they feel like they did a good thing, that's fine.  We're allowed to disagree.  Such is life.<br>
<br>
But don't come and try to compare this to a racist issue because it was a choice that affected EVERYONE and to this day there are many people that don't feel remorse about what they did and on the same breath try to justify it and make ridiculous comparisons.  Don't try to sugarcoat what was done.  In doing so you put yourself in a horizon that has nothing to do with the matter.<br>
<br>
Ishkur Leroux <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=141&stop=160>8</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=161&stop=180>9</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=181&stop=200>10</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=201&stop=220>11</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=221&stop=240>12</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=241&stop=260>13</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=261&stop=280>14</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=281&stop=300>15</a><a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showMessageRange?topicID=731.topic&start=301&stop=320>16